lyrics:
[Verse]
Kashtiyaan paar kare, kinare tak pahuche
Roshni ko lekar, andhere se ladhe
Bharat ka yug badle, liye desh ki raksha mein
Chal diya Modi, desh ke saath mein

[Chorus]
Ane wala pal, ek sapna hai
Desh ko vikas ka, sandesh hai saath
Sangharsh aur samarpan, balidaan se hai jude
Ekta aur vikas ka, yeh nara hai bhare
